General.Name: Trigg Minerals Limited
General.Description: Trigg Minerals Limited engages in the exploration and development of brine-hosted fertilizer minerals in Australia. Its flagship project is the Lake Throssell project, which covers an area of approximately 1,085 square kilometers located near Laverton, Western Australia. The company was formerly known as Trigg Mining Limited and changed its name to Trigg Minerals Limited in August 2022. Trigg Minerals Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Subiaco, Australia.
